data.title: Why is Barisan Nasional in power in Malaysia despite losing the 2018 election?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 3): This is good question. Why? Because Muhyiddin failed to follow Tun Mahathir instruction while he was the Interior Minister under Pakatan Harapan.

Tun Mahathir, as the ex-presiden of UMNO and ex-chairman of BN for 22 years, knows the strength of UMNO/BN. BN is nothing without UMN...
